room_title: Escape room "Dead Red's Debt" by Escape Wapak in Wapakoneta
room_description: Captain Red and her crew of unruly pirates have been cursed by the Legendary Emerald of Truth. You and your team have one hour to pay the eternal debts owed to Red’s mates, and retrieve the Emerald of Truth before the curse is permanent. Do you and your crew have the guts to scour the tavern and uncover the secrets of Dead Red’s Debt?
